<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id78411a43-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s546a–5"><num value="546a–5">§ 546a–5.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id78411a44-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s546a–5/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> Acquisition of lands</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary for the acquisition of land, interests in land, or structures within the scenic area and on the mainland as provided in <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s546a–4">section 546a–4 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id78411a45-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s546a–5/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Other purposes</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In addition to the amounts authorized to be appropriated under subsection (a), there are authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary for the development and implementation of the management plan under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s546a–1/b">section 546a–1(b) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id78411a46-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/106/431/s8">Pub. L. 106–431, § 8</ref>, <date date="2000-11-06">Nov. 6, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/1907">114 Stat. 1907</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
